{"ID":270313, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"313\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs312.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs314.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 313<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">give me my trespasses as I forgive those who trespass against me,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> for I freely forgive<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> all men. If\n  we would secure and cultivate the love of others,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> we must love others,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> even our enemies as well\n  as friends.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Sectarian priests cry out concerning me, and ask, &ldquo;Why is it this babbler<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> gains so many\n  followers,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and retains them?&rdquo; I answer, It is because I possess the principle of love.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> All I can offer\n  the world is a good heart and a good hand.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Saints can testify whether I am willing to lay down my life for my brethren.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> If it has been\n  demonstrated that I have been willing to die for a &ldquo;Mormon,&rdquo; I am bold to declare before Heaven\n  that I am just as ready to die in defending the rights of a Presbyterian, a Baptist, or a good man of\n  any other denomination; for the same principle which would trample upon the rights of the\n  Latter-day Saints would trample upon the rights of the Roman Catholics, or of any other\n  denomination who may be unpopular and too weak to defend themselves.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Love of Liberty<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">It is a love of liberty<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> which inspires my soul&mdash;civil and religious liberty to the whole of the\n  human race. Love of liberty was diffused into my soul by my grandfathers while they dandled me\n  on their knees;<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and shall I want friends? No.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The inquiry is frequently made of me. &ldquo;Wherein do you differ from others in your religious\n  views?&rdquo; In reality and essence we do not differ so far in our religious views, but that we could all\n  drink<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> into one principle of love. One of the grand fundamental principles of &ldquo;Mormonism&rdquo; is to\n  receive truth,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> let it come from whence it may.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">We believe in the Great Elohim who sits enthroned in yonder heavens. So do the Presbyterians.\n  If a skilful mechanic, in taking a welding heat, uses borax, alum, etc., and succeeds in welding\n  together iron or steel more perfectly than any other mechanic, is he not deserving of praise? And if\n  by the principles of truth I succeed in uniting men of all denominations in the bonds of love,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> shall\n  I not have attained a good object?<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If I esteem mankind to be in error, shall I bear them down? No. I will lift them up,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and in their\n  own way too, if I cannot persuade them<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> my way is better; and I will not seek to compel any man\n  to believe as I do, only by the force of reasoning, for truth will cut its own way.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> Do you believe\n  in Jesus Christ and<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107856\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107856)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107856)\">Matt. 6:12,14-15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112622\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112622)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112622)\">3 Ne. 13:11,14-15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111714\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111714)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111714)\">Mosiah 26:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114223\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114223)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114223)\">D&amp;C 64:9-10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109938\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109938)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109938)\">1 Thes. 3:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108785\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108785)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108785)\">John 13:34-35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108821\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108821)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108821)\">John 15:12,17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109378\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109378)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109378)\">Rom. 13:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111561\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111561)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111561)\">Mosiah 4:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114923\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114923)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114923)\">D&amp;C 88:123<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116892\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116892)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116892)\">Moses 7:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citati